name: Nick Every Stash Duffle Bag (GRANDE)
description:
The Nick Every Stash Duffle Bag (GRANDE) is as tough as its name. Constructed of heavy-weight canvas (20oz) and features a WATERPROOF bottom, this bag is prepared to go EVERYwhere.
 
Dimensions [34" x 15" x 12"]
 
It also can be worn as a backpack! 
 
Bag features: 
  • Padded shoulder straps, 
  • 3 Zippered outside pockets
  • Inside security pouch
  • ID holder on front of bag
  • Extra-long vinyl reinforced carry handles
  • Lashing gear rings
  • D rings
  • 3 pouches at the end of the bag. 
Also has two zippers on the main compartment so it can be secured by a lock for additional security.
 
Nick Every Stash Duffle Bag (GRANDE) can be used to carry EVERYthing, EVERYwhere, EVERYday!
